casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Eldon L. BOISSEAU.
No. D-2989.
Supreme Court of the United States
June 12, 2017.
Eldon L. Boisseau, of Wichita, Kansas, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
